ABOUT JUOMAPELI
===============

Read the beginning of juomapeli script:

$ less juomapeli

INSTALLATION
============

Juomapeli requires following programs/stuff to work:

	aplay (alsa sample player)
	Python interpreter

	Something to drink...

USAGE EXAMPLE
=============

Run ./juomapeli to see instructions.

TIPS
====

$ juomapeli 10 me myself I

